title: July Debuts: gesserit is Not Reading anything but IDW this month
description:
"Not Reading Debuts" ( <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/tag/Not+Reading+Debuts" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/tag/Not+Reading+Debuts</a>  ) are part of the <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/tag/Not+Reading" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/tag/Not+Reading</a>  project, and contain all first issues published and/or released during a given month that made an uploader's personal cut.



The month being July 2014 and the uploader being me in this case, obviously.



This instalment contains:



   Ragnarok      #1 - IDW - Classical / Dystopian / Fantasy

   The Last Fall #1 - IDW - Drama / Sci-Fi / War



A mere two new titles from a single publisher, this time, alas. On a positive note, it does balance out the seven new titles, none of which were from this publisher, which I picked last month, though. I certainly did not expect to ever have an Image-less month, but here you are. I went through all of their debuts, as always, but there were definitely fewer than usual, and none of them particularly appealed to me.
